’Щ@bf7efc411445fb88889ef2377c360007da407cf221365107dc4cb75c0008729fЪTitle: title: str length
Path: Flags
Content:
``--grapheme-clusters, -g``
: Count length in grapheme clusters (all visible chars have length 1).
``--utf-8-bytes, -b``
: Count length in UTF-8 bytes (default; all non-ASCII chars have length 2+).
``--chars, -c``
: Count length in chars.
’Щ@b7769cf047263510c177359315db6d23e3b64e6b7db94781b73464974aa02dd2ЩҳTitle: title: str length
Path: Parameters
Content:
``...rest``
: For a data structure input, replace strings at the given cell paths with their length.
